  "text": "We then discuss a noncommutative Majorana condition, that allows coupling of noncommutative gravity to Majorana fermions. The coupling of first order gravity to a Rarita-Schwinger fermion (gravitino), a noncommutative generalization of D = 4, N = 1 supergravity, is discussed in a companion paper [CITATION_1] .",
